      <h3>Careful Service for Coastal, Hillside, and Custom Kitchen Conditions</h3>

      <p>
        Luxury appliances in Rancho Palos Verdes homes may be affected by coastal moisture, hillside installation conditions, outdoor kitchen exposure, custom cabinetry, integrated panels, long water lines, ventilation design, or prior remodeling work. Built-in refrigerators, panel-ready dishwashers, pro-style ranges, wine coolers, and outdoor kitchen appliances should be diagnosed methodically before parts are replaced.
      </p>

      <p>
        When appropriate, we inspect installation conditions, electrical connections, water supply, drainage, ventilation, appliance leveling, seals, airflow, and performance-related components. For properties in areas affected by road conditions, land movement, or restricted access, appointments may require additional access confirmation before dispatch.
